{%- endcall %}

{% call components.section("Style") -%}

  <p>A Search bar can be used in light and dark themes, it includes a form field with placeholder text and a button that is placed on the right.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='lightest') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-blueprint.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component blueprint" style="--inline-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Button</h4>

  <p>A Search bar includes a button so a user can perform a search. A call to action link would only direct a user to the results page without performing the action of searching, so a button must be used instead.</p>

