{% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

  <h4>Long placeholder text</h4>

  <p>Do not write placeholder text too long, it should be short and to the point.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-1.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 1" style="--inline-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Call to action as button</h4>

  <p>Do not replace the button with a call to action.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-2.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 2" style="--inline-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Different style or color</h4>

  <p>Do not use a different button color or style when using a search bar on Red Hat <strong>marketing</strong> websites.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-3.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 3" style="--inline-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Disabled</h4>

  <p>Do not display a disabled button until a user inputs text in the form field. If a user tries to perform a search without any text in the form field, an error icon and text will be displayed instead.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-4.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 4" style="--inline-img-max-width: 872px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Solo button</h4>

  <p>Avoid using the search button on its own without a form field with placeholder text or change the button style and text to something else instead.</p>

  <!-- Temporary Info alert until web component release -->
  <p style="background-color: #e7f1fa; border-top: 2px solid #2b9af3; padding: 16px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">Visit the <a href="https://ux.redhat.com/components/button/" target="_blank">Button</a> component page to learn more about how to use buttons.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-5.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 5" style="--inline-img-max-width: 81px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Rearranging the component</h4>

  <p>Do not rearrange a Search bar by placing the button below the form field or changing its width, even on small screens.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="{{ '/assets/search-bar/search-bar-best-practice-6.svg' | url }}" alt="Search component best practice 6" style="--inline-img-max-width: 360px;">
  {%- endcall %}

{%- endcall %}

